ascend_skill.desc: When Big Welcome or Furrocious Follow-Up are active, Runa can use Woof Woof Blaze. When using Woof Woof Blaze, 60% chance to decrease target's healing received by 30%/40%/50%, and Defense by 6%/12%/18% (effect changes at Lv. 1/50/70, respectively) for 2 turns.
ascend_skill.name: Station Square Mascot

ascend_skill.desc: After using Woof Woof Blaze and activating the effects of Big Welcome, increase target's Fire, Ice, Electric and Wind damage taken by 36% for 2 turns. When activating the effects of Furrocious Follow-Up, increase target's Resonance damage taken by 50% for 2 turns.
ascend_skill.name: Legendary Devotion

ascend_skill.desc: When a foe has a debuff inflicted by Runa, increase target's critical damage taken by 36%, and decrease healing received by 20%.
ascend_skill.name: Trapped in Shibuya

ascend_skill.desc: Increase the skill levels of Woof Woof Blaze and Thief Tactics by 3.
ascend_skill.name: I ♥ Shichi-kun!

ascend_skill.desc: Highlight Enhanced: Increase number of Enthusiastic Fuse stacks inflicted on foes to 4, and increase the maximum number of stacks to 4.
ascend_skill.name: Welcome to Shibuya!

ascend_skill.desc: Increase the skill levels of Welcome Hug and Furrious Bark by 3.
ascend_skill.name: I ♥ Shibuya!

ascend_skill.desc:
At the start of battle, gain Big Welcome and Furrocious Follow-Up for 2 turns.
Extend the duration of debuffs from Welcome Hug, Furrious Bark, and Woof Woof Blaze by 1 turn.
When Big Welcome and Furrocious Follow-Up are both active, increase Woof Woof Blaze's Fire, Ice, Electric, and Wind damage taken effect on all foes by 30%, increase the Resonance damage taken effect on the main target by 60%, and the effects granted by Big Welcome and Furrocious Follow-Up will both activate (the damage taken increase effects do not stack, and the greater effect is applied).
ascend_skill.name: Station Square Superstar

highlight_skill.desc:
Deal Fire damage to all foes equal to 214.7%/236.7%/227.9%/249.9% of Attack.
Permanently inflict 2 Enthusiastic Fuse stacks on foes. Stacks up to 2 times (remove as wave progresses).
Enthusiastic Fuse: When any foe takes Fire, Ice, Electric, or Wind skill damage or Resonance damage, spend 1 Enthusiastic Fuse stack, and increase the damage by 22.9% of Runa's ailment accuracy (up to 53.7%/59.2%/57.0%/62.5%). If Runa's skills and Resonance activate this effect, Enthusiastic Fuse will not be spent.
highlight_skill.name: Highlight

normal_skill.desc:
Deal Fire damage to all foes equal to 73.2%/80.7%/77.7%/85.2% of Attack.
Decrease target's Defense by 15.4% of Runa's ailment accuracy for 2 turns (up to 26.4%/29.1%/28.0%/30.7%). Also, when the target of this effect takes Fire, Ice, Electric, or Ice skill damage, decrease Defense by 26.4%/26.4%/28.0%/28.0% more. The Defense decrease effects from this skill and Furrious Bark do not stack.
Also, 50% chance to inflict Burn on the target, and gain Big Welcome for 2 turns.
normal_skill.name: Welcome Hug

normal_skill.desc:
Deal Fire damage to 1 foe equal to 170.8%/188.3%/181.3%/198.8% of Attack.
Decrease target's Defense by 14.6%/14.6%/15.5%/15.5% + 31.4% of Runa's ailment accuracy (up to 53.7%/59.2%/57.0%/62.5%) for 2 turns. The Defense decrease effects from this skill and Welcome Hug do not stack.
Also, gain Furrocious Follow-Up for 2 turns.
normal_skill.name: Furrious Bark

normal_skill.desc:
Usable when Big Welcome or Furrocious Follow-Up are active, and activates various effects based on which is active. If both effects are active at the same time, prioritize Big Welcome.
Remove Big Welcome and Furrocious Follow-Up after effect activates.
Big Welcome: Deal Fire damage to all foes equal to 109.8%/109.8%/116.6%/116.6% of Attack. This skill's damage is counted as a Resonance.
Increase target's damage taken by 24% of Runa's ailment accuracy (up to 41.0%/45.2%/43.5%/47.7%), and Fire, Ice, Electric and Wind damage taken by 20.5%/22.6%/21.8%/23.9% for 2 turns.
Furrocious Follow-Up: Deal Fire damage to 1 foe equal to 219.6%/219.6%/233.1%/233.1% of Attack. This skill's damage is counted as a Resonance.
Increase target's damage taken by 34.3% of Runa's ailment accuracy (up to 58.6%/64.6%/62.2%/68.2%), and Resonance damage taken by 39.0%/43.0%/41.4%/45.4% for 2 turns.
normal_skill.name: Woof Woof Blaze

passive_skill.desc: During battle, increase Runa's Attack by 60.0% of her ailment accuracy.
passive_skill.name: Peppy Guard Dog

passive_skill.desc: When Runa inflicts a debuff on a foe with a skill, increase her Attack by 33.0% for 1 turn. When an ally deals Fire, Ice, Electric or Wind damage or Resonance damage, grant them the same Attack increase effect.
passive_skill.name: Faithful Dog
